bug me or Tiekith.
2) As there's a syllabus obj, I'm taking both the new and
old syllabus out of the ghelp.  It's going to be pruned.
Short, I say! Short!
3) Recruiters.  There's now a ghelp 8 recruiters.  That
covers the requirements, etc, to become a recruiter.  
Recruiters are the spiffy people who have guild permission
and help out seekers or new members.  I'll think up some
incentive to become one later, but there will probably
be rewards for doing a good job at this.
Oh, and you.  Yes, you.  RP.  That's not a request, it's
an order.  =P  I'd like to see activity.  Come on, guys.
You finally have a chance for IC advancement, and to get
some RP going.  Carpe diem!  Plus, you get questpoints.
Double bonus.  Take advantage of it.
That's all for now...I'll think up something else to bother
everyone about later, probably. 
-Jeph
